Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十月二日  傍晚五時二十五分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姐姐也沒起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比往常更早地離開了那個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我曾經在那附近的天空中飛翔過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我登上神社的石階
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了那女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像  看到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡做壞事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被松尾大人責罵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（註：松尾大人，日本酒釀造的神，被供奉在釀酒的店裡）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我什麼也沒有做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐  今天也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為鄰居家的大爺說今晚還想喝點酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿的那是糙米酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是今晚再喝點的話  血壓就能降下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  其實就是健康飲料之類的東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長說要用明年釀的酒準備正規的酒場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快點把明年的酒場籌備起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐  你用香水了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可能是洗髮水的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釀酒的時候我是絕對不會用香水的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎  你的鼻子可真靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是老闆的嫡子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  味道不怎麼好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  喝慣了就會覺得好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起碼…我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧小姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年要開始正規地釀造糙米酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她一開始好像不是很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來鄰居家大爺身體好起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就開始有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說九月份之後有很多轉學生要來了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山那邊的工廠似乎有所行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是希望我繼承家業的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是討厭酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是…我小時候偷偷喝了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有點噁心罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了你那代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道這裡的水還能不能用來釀酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該由姐姐她繼承的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}很傷腦筋吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  能借我抄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對轉學生要親切些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管  跟別人說去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  怎麼一副沒睡醒的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚根本沒睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  看  大神居然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B班的大神？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙好像已經兩週沒來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  老師來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不坐到位子上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快坐好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}…逐漸變得明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}…教科書53頁  有好好看著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也來了這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  神社背後有這樣一條路的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  只是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是在夢裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢魘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我說  那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}別淘氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊  這是體罰  體罰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}德永
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}要是出手打他你就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是啦是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古森  今天放學後來一下校長室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來做隨堂測試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是A班的古森太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…還真的叫太郎啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是轉學到B班的中島匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次到我家去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多事情想請教你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說吧  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  古森同學你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個月開始臨床心理老師換人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是東京大學的平田篤司老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個月開始負責你的心理諮詢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的心理老師也是使用這房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去職員室了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了叫我一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的風景可真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有「日本」風味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有和以前的心理老師交接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是經常在白天感到睡意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的  時常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你把夢都記錄下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都錄在磁帶裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後能讓我聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不願意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須先好好整理下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一年前發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是讓古森同學你感到痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:47.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[水天町2名兒童被綁架]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[犯人因發生事故喪生]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[在警察的眼皮底下……贖金交付失敗]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[2名兒童失蹤]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[父母的願望落空]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:02.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}[2兒童被綁架事件：行蹤不明4日後  弟弟太郎安全獲救]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大神同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第一次見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從東京搬過來的中島匡幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以直接叫你的名字「信」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  還真夠煩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常有人這樣說我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我性格就是這樣  沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  平田老師…您會用催眠療法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  一旦被催眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經忘記了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能記起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想回憶起來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喪失了部分記憶  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對催眠療法不是特別認同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催眠有時會出現自己捏造的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回憶起什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校嘛  我只有興致來了才會去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再纏著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我有事想問問你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於A班的太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你很憎恨他？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和十一年前信你的父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎  只是想問問你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天白天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不理不睬的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說只要訓練一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就可以自由的在夢中行動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.49,0:24:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是弗朗西斯·克里克的夢的解析認為
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.49,0:24:42.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（註：弗朗西斯·克里克(Francis Crick)，英國分子生物學家。\N在DNA分子雙螺旋結構的發現，\N以及在揭開生物遺傳訊息秘密方面作出貢獻。）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢不過是把記錄在大腦新皮質中的無意義記憶消除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.71,0:24:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其本身是毫無意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.12,0:24:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於克里克來說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.35,0:24:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識不過是一種發生於腦內的40赫茲共鳴現象而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:25:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢  夢的形態  夢的世界  幽世
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.96,0:25:04.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\an5\pos(640,475)}--眼動脫敏與再加工療法--
